</tr>
<tr>
<td width="50%" style="border-right: 1px dotted #aaa;">Regular army: &lt;55,000,<br />
Volunteers: &lt;100,000</td>
<td width="50%" style="padding-left: 0.25em;">Regular army: 60,000,<br />
86 warships and frigates</td>
</tr>
