</tr>
<tr>
<td width="50%" style="border-right: 1px dotted #aaa;">Military deaths: unknown,<br />
Civilian deaths: &lt;100,000</td>
<td width="50%" style="padding-left: 0.25em;">Military deaths: 57,000 (37,000 combat; 20,000 yellow fever)<br />
Civilian deaths: ~25,000</td>
